          "lecciones": [
            {
              "code": 110,
              "order": 1,
              "slug": {
                "es": "banking-and-money",
                "en": "banking-and-money"
              },
              "display": {
                "es": "Banca y dinero",
                "en": "Banking and Money"
              },
              "view": {
                "es": "| Vocabulario |\n| --- |\n| account<br>cuenta |\n| balance<br>balance/saldo |\n| bank<br>banco |\n| bank charges<br>gastos bancarios/comisión |\n| bank machine (ATM)<br>cajero automático |\n| bank teller<br>cajero |\n| bills<br>billetes |\n| branch<br>sucursal |\n| cash<br>dinero |\n| check<br>cheque |\n| coins<br>monedas |\n| credit card<br>tarjeta de crédito |\n| currency<br>moneda |\n| deposit<br>ingreso |\n| exchange rate<br>el cambio |\n| in cash<br>en efectivo |\n| interest<br>interés |\n| interest rate<br>tasa de interés |\n| loan<br>préstamo |\n| overdraft<br>la cuenta al descubierto |\n| small change<br>suelto |\n| signature<br>firma |\n| statement<br>estado de cuenta |\n| traveler's check<br>cheques de viajero |\n| wire transfer<br>transferencia bancaria |\n| withdrawal<br>retirada |\n| **Verbs** |\n| to charge<br>cobrar |\n| to deposit<br>ingresar |\n| to sign<br>firmar |\n| to withdraw<br>retirar, sacar |\n\n## Useful Phrases (Frases útiles)\n\n> **Example:** Is there a bank machine near here?\n> **Translation:** (¿Hay un cajero automático cerca de aquí?)\n\n> **Example:** Where is there a bank?\n> **Translation:** (¿Dónde hay un banco?)\n\n> **Example:** Where can I change money?\n> **Translation:** (¿Dónde puedo cambiar dinero?)\n\n> **Example:** Can you change money for me?\n> **Translation:** (¿Me puede cambiar dinero?)\n\n> **Example:** What is the exchange rate?\n> **Translation:** (¿Qué es el cambio?)\n\n> **Example:** Do you accept traveler's checks [credit cards]?\n> **Translation:** (¿Acepta cheques de viajero [tarjetas de crédito]?)\n\n> **Example:** Can I cash a check?\n> **Translation:** (¿Puedo cambiar un cheque?)\n\n> **Example:** Is there a commission/fee?\n> **Translation:** (¿Cobra comisión?)\n\n> **Example:** Where do I sign?\n> **Translation:** (¿Dónde firmo?)\n\n## Dialogue (Diálogo)\n\n**Bank teller:**\n\n> **Example:** Good morning, how can I help you today?\n> **Translation:** <br>Buenos días. ¿Cómo le puedo ayudar?\n\n**Anne:**\n\n> **Example:** Hello. I would like to make a wire transfer from my bank account to this number, please.\n> **Translation:** <br>Hola. Quiero hacer una transferencia de mi cuenta bancaria a esta cuenta, por favor.\n\n**Bank teller:**\n\n> **Example:** Okay. Can you give me your I.D. card for identification?\n> **Translation:** <br>Vale. ¿Me puede dejar un carnet de identidad?\n\n**Anne:**\n\n> **Example:** Yes, here it is.\n> **Translation:** <br>Sí, aquí lo tiene.\n\n**Bank teller:**\n\n> **Example:** There is a $3 charge for wire transfers.\n> **Translation:** <br>Hay una comisión bancaria de $3 para transferencias.\n\n**Anne:**\n\n> **Example:** Okay, that's fine.\n> **Translation:** <br>Vale, está bien.\n\n**Bank teller:**\n\n> **Example:** Here is your copy of the wire transfer.\n> **Translation:** <br>Aquí tiene la copia de la transferencia.\n\n**Anne:**\n\n> **Example:** Thank you, good-bye.\n> **Translation:** <br>Gracias, adiós.",
                "en": "### Vocabulary\n\n| English |\n| --- |\n| account |\n| balance |\n| bank |\n| bank charges |\n| bank machine (ATM) |\n| bank teller |\n| bills |\n| branch |\n| cash |\n| check |\n| coins |\n| credit card |\n| currency |\n| deposit |\n| exchange rate |\n| in cash |\n| interest |\n| interest rate |\n| loan |\n| overdraft |\n| small change |\n| signature |\n| statement |\n| traveler's check |\n| wire transfer |\n| withdrawal |\n| **Verbs** |\n| to charge |\n| to deposit |\n| to sign |\n| to withdraw |\n\n## Useful Phrases\n\n> **Example:** Is there a bank machine near here?\n\n> **Example:** Where is there a bank?\n\n> **Example:** Where can I change money?\n\n> **Example:** Can you change money for me?\n\n> **Example:** What is the exchange rate?\n\n> **Example:** Do you accept traveler's checks [credit cards]?\n\n> **Example:** Can I cash a check?\n\n> **Example:** Is there a commission/fee?\n\n> **Example:** Where do I sign?\n\n## Dialogue\n\n**Bank teller:**\n\n> **Example:** Good morning, how can I help you today?\n\n**Anne:**\n\n> **Example:** Hello. I would like to make a wire transfer from my bank account to this number, please.\n\n**Bank teller:**\n\n> **Example:** Okay. Can you give me your I.D. card for identification?\n\n**Anne:**\n\n> **Example:** Yes, here it is.\n\n**Bank teller:**\n\n> **Example:** There is a $3 charge for wire transfers.\n\n**Anne:**\n\n> **Example:** Okay, that's fine.\n\n**Bank teller:**\n\n> **Example:** Here is your copy of the wire transfer.\n\n**Anne:**\n\n> **Example:** Thank you, good-bye."
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
