              },
              "display": {
                "es": "En un hotel",
                "en": "In a Hotel"
              },
              "view": {
                "es": "| Vocabulario |\n| --- |\n| reservation<br>reserva |\n| reception<br>recepción |\n| lobby<br>vestíbulo |\n| full board<br>pensión completa |\n| half board<br>media pensión |\n| single/double room<br>habitación individual/doble |\n| vacancies<br>habitaciones libres |\n| no vacancy<br>completo |\n| porter, bellhop (US)<br>portero |\n| **Verbos** |\n| to check in<br>registrarse |\n| to check out<br>pagar e irse del hotel |\n| to stay<br>quedarse |\n\n## Useful Phrases (Frases útiles)\n\n> **Example:** I have a reservation.\n> **Translation:** (Tengo una reserva.)\n\n> **Example:** I would like a room for the night.\n> **Translation:** (Quisiera una habitación para la noche.)\n\n> **Example:** Are there any rooms available?\n> **Translation:** (¿Hay habitaciones disponibles?)\n\n> **Example:** Would you like a single or double room?\n> **Translation:** (¿Le gustaría una habitación individual o doble?)\n\n> **Example:** How long will you be staying?\n> **Translation:** (¿Cuánto tiempo va a quedarse?)\n\n> **Example:** Does the room have a private bath?\n> **Translation:** (¿La habitación tiene un baño privado?)\n\n> **Example:** Is breakfast [dinner] included?\n> **Translation:** (¿El desayuno [la cena] está incluido?)\n\n> **Example:** What time is breakfast [dinner] served?\n> **Translation:** (¿A qué hora sirven el desayuno [la cena]?)\n\n> **Example:** Please charge it to my room [bill].\n> **Translation:** (Por favor cárguelo a mi habitación [cuenta].)\n\n> **Example:** Is there parking?\n> **Translation:** (¿Hay aparcamiento?)\n\n> **Example:** How much is the room?\n> **Translation:** (¿Cuánto cuesta la habitación?)\n\n> **Example:** What time is check out?\n> **Translation:** (¿Cuándo hay que dejar el hotel?)\n\n> **Example:** Do you need the porter to assist you with your bags?\n> **Translation:** (¿Necesita al portero para que le ayude con su equipaje?)\n\n> **Example:** Here is your room key. Your room number is...\n> **Translation:** (Aquí está su llave. Su habitación es...)\n\n> **Example:** My room key, please.\n> **Translation:** (La llave por favor.)\n\n> **Example:** If you need anything, dial 0 for reception.\n> **Translation:** (Si necesita cualquier cosa, marque el 0 para contactar con recepción.)\n\n> **Example:** Can you please call me a taxi?\n> **Translation:** (¿Puede llamarme un taxi por favor?)\n\n> **Example:** May I have some more towels?\n> **Translation:** (¿Puedo tener algunas toallas más?)\n\n> **Example:** Please clean the room.\n> **Translation:** (Por favor, limpie mi habitación.)\n\n> **Example:** Please do not disturb.\n> **Translation:** (Por favor, no molestar.)\n\n> **Example:** Is there a safe in the room?\n> **Translation:** (¿Hay una caja fuerte en la habitación?)",
                "en": "### Vocabulary\n\n| English |\n| --- |\n| full board |\n| half board |\n| lobby |\n| no vacancy |\n| porter, bellhop (US) |\n| reception |\n| reservation |\n| single/double room |\n| vacancies |\n| **Verbs** |\n| to check in |\n| to check out |\n| to stay |\n\n### Useful Phrases\n\n> **Example:** I have a reservation.\n\n> **Example:** I would like a room for the night.\n\n> **Example:** Are there any rooms available?\n\n> **Example:** Would you like a single or double room?\n\n> **Example:** How long will you be staying?\n\n> **Example:** Does the room have a private bath?\n\n> **Example:** Is breakfast [dinner] included?\n\n> **Example:** What time is breakfast [dinner] served?\n\n> **Example:** Please charge it to my room [bill].\n\n> **Example:** Is there parking?\n\n> **Example:** How much is the room?\n\n> **Example:** What time is check out?\n\n> **Example:** Do you need the porter to assist you with your bags?\n\n> **Example:** Here is your room key. Your room number is...\n\n> **Example:** My room key, please.\n\n> **Example:** If you need anything, dial 0 for reception.\n\n> **Example:** Can you please call me a taxi?\n\n> **Example:** May I have some more towels?\n\n> **Example:** Please clean the room.\n\n> **Example:** Please do not disturb.\n\n> **Example:** Is there a safe in the room?"
              }
