                "es": "| Vocabulario |\n| --- |\n| apple<br>manzana |\n| avocado<br>aguacate |\n| banana<br>plátano |\n| carrot<br>zanahoria |\n| cherries<br>cerezas |\n| cucumber<br>pepino |\n| eggplant<br>berenjena |\n| grapes<br>uvas |\n| kiwi<br>kiwi |\n| lettuce<br>lechuga |\n| mushroom<br>champiñón |\n| nectarine<br>nectarina |\n| onion<br>cebolla |\n| orange<br>naranja |\n| pear<br>pera |\n| peach<br>melocotón |\n| pepper<br>pimiento |\n| plum<br>ciruela |\n| potato<br>patata |\n| spinach<br>espinacas |\n| strawberries<br>fresas |\n| tomato<br>tomate |\n\n## Useful expressions (Frases útiles)\n\n> **Example:** Hello. Can I help you?\n> **Translation:** (Hola. ¿Puedo ayudarle?)\n\n> **Example:** Here are the bags.\n> **Translation:** (Aquí están las bolsas.)\n\n> **Example:** These apples are $1.25 a kilo.\n> **Translation:** (Estas manzanas están a $1.25 el kilo.)\n\n> **Example:** Would you like me to cut the leaves off for you?\n> **Translation:** (¿Quiere que le corte las hojas? )\n\n> **Example:** Lettuce is on offer today. 2 heads of lettuce for the price of one.\n> **Translation:** (Hay una oferta de lechugas hoy. 2 lechugas al precio de una.)\n\n> **Example:** We have these strawberries on sale today. A box of 1 kilo for only $2.99.\n> **Translation:** (Tenemos las fresas de oferta hoy. Una caja de un kilo por solo $2.99.)",
                "en": "| Vocabulary |\n| --- |\n| apple |\n| avocado |\n| banana |\n| carrot |\n| cherries |\n| cucumber |\n| eggplant |\n| grapes |\n| kiwi |\n| lettuce |\n| mushroom |\n| nectarine |\n| onion |\n| orange |\n| pear |\n| peach |\n| pepper |\n| plum |\n| potato |\n| spinach |\n| strawberries |\n| tomato |\n\n## Useful expressions\n\n> **Example:** Hello. Can I help you?\n\n> **Example:** Here are the bags.\n\n> **Example:** These apples are $1.25 a kilo.\n\n> **Example:** Would you like me to cut the leaves off for you?\n\n> **Example:** Lettuce is on offer today. 2 heads of lettuce for the price of one.\n\n> **Example:** We have these strawberries on sale today. A box of 1 kilo for only $2.99."
